## 2.3.3 Using Basic Functions in R {.compact}

:::: {.two-col-lean}
::: {.col}
```{webr}
#| autorun: false

x <- c(10, 3, 8, 25, 7)

# Find the maximum and minimum values
max(x)
min(x)

# Sort the vector
sort(x)                       # ascending order
sort(x, decreasing = TRUE)    # descending order

# Find the order (ranks) of elements
order(x)
```
